Following my impulses

67
00:07:03,488 --> 00:07:07,988
茨の道を裸足で駆け抜けてく
Running through the thorny path barefoot

68
00:07:09,188 --> 00:07:12,688
凛と咲き誇る花でありたい
I want to be a flower blooming proudly

69
00:07:12,888 --> 00:07:16,388
あなただけを求めて
Seeking only you

70
00:07:17,188 --> 00:07:20,488
会いに行くの どんな遠く
I'm going to see you, no matter how far

71
00:07:20,688 --> 00:07:23,888
離れていても見つけ出せる
Even if we're apart, I can find you

72
00:07:24,388 --> 00:07:27,588
暗い世界も怖くない
I'm not afraid of the dark world

73
00:07:27,788 --> 00:07:30,788
あなたを感じるから
Because I feel you

74
00:07:31,288 --> 00:07:34,488
全て失ったっていい
It's fine even if I lose everything

75
00:07:34,688 --> 00:07:38,988
二度と戻らない So Secret Garden
I'll never go back, So Secret Garden

76
