今はどんな花とも群れないの
I won't mingle with any flower now

77
00:08:11,488 --> 00:08:14,888
あなただけを求めて
Seeking only you

78
00:08:15,488 --> 00:08:18,588
霞の向こう 私を呼ぶ
Beyond the mist, you call me

79
00:08:18,788 --> 00:08:21,988
鮮やかに燃える 強気なバラ
A strong rose burning vividly

80
00:08:24,188 --> 00:08:27,688
凛と咲き誇る花でありたい
I want to be a flower blooming proudly

81
00:08:27,888 --> 00:08:31,288
やっとここで出会えた
Finally, we met here

82
00:08:32,188 --> 00:08:35,588
あなたとなら この身体が
If it's with you, even if this body

83
00:08:35,688 --> 00:08:38,888
壊されたってかまわない
Is broken, I don't care

84
00:08:39,388 --> 00:08:42,688
棘に触れたら傷つくわ
You'll get hurt if you touch the thorns

85
00:08:42,788 --> 00:08:45,988
その覚悟があるのね
You have that resolve, don't you?

86
00:08:46,288 --> 00:08:49,488
手を取り合えば広がる
If we hold hands, it will expand

87
00:08:49,588 --> 00:08:53,988
誰も知らない So Sacred Universe
The So Sacred Universe that no one knows

88
